snippet.title: Escape The Pacific -  Sailing
snippet.description:
This short video shows our Sailing system as is implemented in this early (0.0.0.18 alpha) stage of development. 

For more information see: https://gamers4gamersteam.com/sailing/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/G4GTeam
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Gamers4GamersTeam

We will upload more videos about other game features soon.
